{"tid":1922841,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"請教各位絲打：《戒j定j你好》","createTime":"2020-03-12T20:16:16.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-01T07:26:36.000Z","uid":348825,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"9e02745fdf532300a9523b8b37ad998a1a25e80c","tid":1922841,"uid":348825,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-12T20:16:16.000Z","msg":"我知我咁問好變態<br />\n其實係女人都想男人唔好打咁多丁既<br />\n作為男人自己明，打完之後係會好攰<br />\n之後個腦正係行到6-7成<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/30.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n但真係好想問問，女生們<br />\n如果喺以下情況：<br />\n1）條囝未同你一齊<br />\n2）條囝想同你共度一生既、不求一剎那既愛<br />\n3）你樣令身材正<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">如果有得比你地揀<br />\n你地會想佢睇日本妹自己解決<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">定係對住自己張相打j</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">認真你會點揀。</span><br />\n</span></strong><br />\n自問小弟鍾意緊個個人<br />\n其實外在既有齊，天使既臉孔<br />\n直徑長過貨櫃車車胎既波波<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n又長又白既美腿<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一般男人想要既，喺齊哂到。<br />\n<br />\n但我鍾意既係佢性格<br />\n佢成熟得黎又唔會顯得世故<br />\n你會喺佢身上搵到一份純粹與善良<br />\n但佢諗野又係成熟既。<br />\n<br />\n最放不下既，係同佢有過既故事<br />\n喺人生既絕望谷中<br />\n佢伸手將我拉起<br />\n那怕再短暫，亦刻骨銘心。<br />\n<br />\n其實，就實然性以及平心而論<br />\n為左佢戒丁係應份既。<br />\n但面臨血氣方剛之際<br />\n有時控制唔到<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">再加上，佢會唔會唔係介意自己打丁<br />\n而係唔係對住自己打丁？</span></strong><br />\n</span><br />\n當然，<br />\n我明白性同愛係好難分得開<br />\n但自己鍾意既，如果係擁有內在美既佢<br />\n對住佢起機絕對無問題<br />\n但就係唔太想<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/39.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以有時stalk佢ig都避免往肩膀以下既地方停留<br />\n好驚自己會起機。。。。<br />\n<br />\n然而，<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">巴絲們，細佬好迷啊</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/21.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de9a6cad6e74ab563771d01bb14d7f0ea919ff11","tid":1922841,"uid":348825,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-12T20:21:31.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb089f01a332e223a145a5ae77622f5dd1338b9a","tid":1922841,"uid":64343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-12T20:23:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />cls"},{"pid":"9da828ecdccca2141ebfac9c85f97ebb3d5baea5","tid":1922841,"uid":348825,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fb089f01a332e223a145a5ae77622f5dd1338b9a","tid":1922841,"uid":64343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-12T20:23:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />cls"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-12T20:29:44.000Z","msg":"我都知架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/27.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ccd058ecc8fcb773ee11f742d7351bad08fba118","tid":1922841,"uid":64343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9da828ecdccca2141ebfac9c85f97ebb3d5baea5","tid":1922841,"uid":348825,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fb089f01a332e223a145a5ae77622f5dd1338b9a","tid":1922841,"uid":64343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-12T20:23:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />cls"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-12T20:29:44.000Z","msg":"我都知架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/27.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-12T20:31:21.000Z","msg":"弱智就驗下個腦啦"},{"pid":"da4ae6aefce9ce3169acf0834eb52d9373ec8ab2","tid":1922841,"uid":348825,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ccd058ecc8fcb773ee11f742d7351bad08fba118","tid":1922841,"uid":64343,"like":0,"d